'''Magyar Tolkien Társaság''' (Hungarian: '''Hungarian Tolkien Society''') is the [[Tolkien Societies|Tolkien Society]] in Hungary.

==Publications==
HTS started publishing ''Lassi Laurië'' in the mid 2000s. In 2016 it became an online publication, and it currently has two issues a year.
